  m_text: "My name is Cesar Strandberg, and I\u2019m a student at Lund University.
    This project has been my playground for the past months where I have tried my
    best to recreate the feeling of the american psycho movie.I hope you enjoy! And
    yes, I\u2019ve done my best to avoid making it too cringe :)\nGitHub: cesarstrandberg"
